headline: Invitation Homes Reports Fourth Quarter 2024 and Full Year 2024 Results
summary: DALLAS, February 26, 2025--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes" or the "Company"), the nation’s premier single-family home leasing and management company, today announced its Fourth Quarter ("Q4") 2024 and Full Year ("FY") 2024 financial and operating results.
